snippet.title: Emma & Jannie Pretend Play Learn Colors w/ Fun Colorful Playmat for Kids
snippet.description:
Emma and Jannie pretend play learning colors with fun colorful playmat made for kids! They setup the playmat and jump around while learning the colors on the fun playmat. Uncle John also plays the mixing color game with them and also the floor is lava! Have fun watching this fun educational video for children.
